    {
      "title": "Going somewhere: 去 + place",
      "pattern": "我去医院。",
      "note": "去 (qù) = to go. Put the destination right after 去. To say how you get there, add the transport before: 我坐出租车去医院。"
    },
    {
      "title": "Asking where: 在哪儿？",
      "pattern": "医院在哪儿？",
      "note": "哪儿 (nǎr) = where. 在 + 哪儿 asks for location. Answer: [place] 在 [location]. 医院在右边 = The hospital is on the right."
    },
    {
      "title": "From … to …: 从…到…",
      "pattern": "从北京到上海坐飞机。",
      "note": "从 (cóng) = from, 到 (dào) = to. This pattern shows the starting and ending point of travel."
    }
